##################################
###### My Trigger Studies     ####
##################################

- Most of the things here are based on the new openHLT (https://github.com/jiafulow/HLTrigger-HLTanalyzers-test-openHLT) 
- Trigger Rates with: test/GetRates.py (you need log files from openHLT Filter)
- My modify menu: test/hlt_DiffHT_717_v90_MC.py
- Datasets and multicrab jobs: test/multicrab.cfg

Enjoy it!


To reproduce these results:
 export SCRAM_ARCH=slc6_amd64_gcc481
 cmsrel CMSSW_7_1_7
 cd CMSSW_7_1_7/src
 cmsenv
 git cms-addpkg HLTrigger/Configuration
 git cms-merge-topic perrotta:hltTemplatesForRun2In717
 scramv1 b -j 18
 cd HLTrigger/Configuration/test/
 ./cmsDriver.csh 
 cd ../../../
 mkdir MyTrigger
 git clone https://github.com/alefisico/myTriggerStudies.git MyTrigger/myTriggerStudies
 cd MyTrigger/myTriggerStudies/
 git checkout v717
 cd -
 git clone git@github.com:jiafulow/HLTrigger-HLTanalyzers-test-openHLT.git MyTrigger/myTriggerStudies/test/openHLT
 scramv1 b -j 18
 cmsenv 



HLT Menu used:
 hltGetConfiguration /dev/CMSSW_7_1_1/HLT/V90 --full --offline --mc --unprescale --process TEST --globaltag auto:startup_GRun --no-output > hlt.py

